data.description: This 4/2.5/2 GHO Dahlia courtyard pool home is a stunning model-like property with numerous upgrades and features. Located in the gated Lily's Cay neighborhood, this home boasts a screened salt-water pool with double waterfall and travertine lanai. The interior showcases a gourmet kitchen with custom cabinets, granite countertops, a huge island and a 5 burner gas range with a vented hood. The spacious living area has 10-12' ceilings, wood plank style tile flooring, a wine bar and custom millwork finishes throughout. The bedrooms have custom wood closet systems for extra storage and convenience. This home also has PGT impact windows, hurricane rated garage door, tankless gas water heater, natural gas for cooking and a concrete block construction. Enjoy the fantastic outdoor space and the proximity to the beach, hospital, shops and restaurants. This home has it all and is ready for you to move in!
